releases.title: Live 060708
releases.notes:
From Cylob's Bandcamp page.

Text on page:
"Live 060708 is a collection of three live sets recorded in December 2006, December 2007 and October 2008. The first two sets were performed in a dance-floor setting and are centered around the album "Trojan Fader Style". They give the listener a chance to hear the raw sound of the Cylob Music System in action, live and direct. The third set is a more sedate affair, having been performed at the ambient evening of the Finnish electronic music festival Mansedanse. The pieces come from the albums "Cylobian Sunset", "Ambient News" and "Formant Potaton" among others.

Although most of the music featured will be familiar to Cylob devotees, there are several tracks which appear exclusively on this release. Those that have featured on studio albums are presented here in alternative versions: there are additional melodies, some parts are played or programmed live and the mixes are different.
